{
    "T14n1282u_001:0": " Pratimālakṣaṇavivaraṇam",
    "T14n1282u_001:1": " oṃ ..........bhagavatā yadevoktaṃ buddhākṛtau phalam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:2": " lakṣaṇaṃ buddhamūrttīnāṃ tadevātrāpi likhyate ||",
    "T14n1282u_001:3": " sarvalakṣaṇasaṃpūrṇā pratimā sukhadāyikā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:4": " tadvihīnā yadā yasmāt dānta(yā syādante )",
    "T14n1282u_001:5": " duḥkhapradāyika ||",
    "T14n1282u_001:6": " kiṃ tatsukham |",
    "T14n1282u_001:7": " tadāha - yāvantaḥ paramāṇavo bhagavatstūpeṣu bimbeṣu vā tatkarturdivi bhūtale ca niyataṃ tāvanti rājyā....rūpāsanādhisaṃpadamvinā bhuktvā ca sarvaṃ....prāpte janmajarāvipattirahitaṃ prāpnoti bauddha padam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:8": " ato rūpakāyasya lakṣaṇamāha - tatra samyaksambuddhānāṃ mahāvajradharāṇāñca dairghyeṇa kāyasya bāhudvayapārśvaprasāritavyāmenāpi kiṃ pramāṇam",
    "T14n1282u_001:9": " svakīyāṅgulena sārddhadvādaśāṅgulastālistena pañcaviṃśatyadhikaśatāṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:10": " locanādidevīnāṃ dvādaśāṅgulastālastena navatālenāṣṭottaraśatāṅgulāyāmo vyāmaśca |",
    "T14n1282u_001:11": " bodhisattvānāñca dvādaśāṅgulairdaśatālakameva |",
    "T14n1282u_001:12": " kharvvalambodarakrodhānāñca ṣaṇṇavatyaṅgulamaṣṭatālena |",
    "T14n1282u_001:13": " lalatkrodhānāṃ tu daśatālena viṃśatyuttaraśatāṅgulāyāmavyāmābhyāṃ sarvāṅgopāṅgoditaṃ jñātavyam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:14": " \"śāsturddharmadeśanāgamanasamaye śāriputro bhagavantametadavocat - bhagavan bhagavatā vinā śrāddhaiḥ kulaputraiḥ kuladuhitṛbhiśca kathaṃ pratipattavyam",
    "T14n1282u_001:15": " bhagavānāha - śāriputra !mayi gate parinirvṛte vā nyagrodhaparimaṇḍalaṃ yāvadvyāmaṃ tāvat kāyaṃ yāvatkāyaṃ tāvadvyāmaṃ pūjāsatkārārthaṃ pratimā kartavyā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:16": " sarvaṅgaupāṅgāvayavasthaulyalāvaṇyalālityasalīlatvaṃ saptotsadamahāhanutvaṃ chatrākāraśiraḥskandhasusaṃsthitoṣṇīṣatvādisusaṃsthānā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:17": " tatrāyāme vistārotsedhasandhibandhananirgamaiḥ pramāṇaṃ buddhamūrttīnāṃ bodhisattvānāṃ ca ' '",
    "T14n1282u_001:19": " iti vacanāt |",
    "T14n1282u_001:20": " tatra lāvaṇyaṃ snigdhaca(dha)rmatā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:21": " lālityaṃ manoharatā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:22": " salīlatvaṃ tribhaṅgatvādiguṇena |",
    "T14n1282u_001:23": " saptotsadeti saptāvayavāḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:24": " utsadā ucchrayā unnatāśceti paryāyāḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:25": " katame pādadvayaṃ hastadvayaṃ skandhadvayaṃ grīvā ceti |",
    "T14n1282u_001:26": " aparaṃ prasiddhameva kiñcidunnatirucche(tse)dhaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:27": " tatra caturaṅgulamuṣṇīṣaṃ keśasthānañca tathaiva lalāṭanāsikadhaścibukāntaṃ caturvādhikacaturaṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:28": " etenārddhatrayodaśīmātrā mukhabhāgaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:29": " cibukaṃ dvyaṅgulaṃ bhavet |",
    "T14n1282u_001:30": " āyāmanirgamābhyāñcaiva caturaṅgulamiṣyate |",
    "T14n1282u_001:31": " caturaṅgulau kapolavākarṇamūlādvinirgatau |",
    "T14n1282u_001:32": " cakṣuradhaścarmaṇo'",
    "T14n1282u_001:33": " dhobhāgā hanuḥ syāt dvyaṅgulotsedho vistārāt dvyaṃgulaśca saḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:34": " bodhisattvāpekṣaḥ so'",
    "T14n1282u_001:35": " dhikaḥ paripūrṇaḥ syānmahāsiṃhahanuryathā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:36": " saṃbuddhamahāvajradharāṇāṃ kiñcidunnata ityarthaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:37": " krodhānāṃ tu cipiṭo vistārādhikaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:38": " adharo dvyaṅgulāyāmo nirgamotsedhamātrikaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:39": " aṅgulyāstṛtīyabhāgo mātrika iti |",
    "T14n1282u_001:40": " adharamadhyaṃ bimbaphalavat |",
    "T14n1282u_001:41": " ekāṅgule sṛkkaṇī |",
    "T14n1282u_001:42": " caturaṅgulāyāmaṃ vaktraṃ yathopapannavinyāsaśca catvāriṃśaddaśanānāṃ rājadadantādikrameṇa |",
    "T14n1282u_001:43": " uttaroṣṭho'",
    "T14n1282u_001:44": " ṅgulārdhaścaturyavo nirgamotsedhābhyām |",
    "T14n1282u_001:45": " nāsāgrā'dharaṣṭāṅgulastribhāgā praṇīlākārā śmaśrumathyā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:46": " godhiḥ nāsādvyaṅgulavistārā sārddhāṅgulonnatā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:47": " buddhānāṃ kiñcidadhikā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:48": " atikrodhānāṃ kiñciccipiṭā pārśvanirgatā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:49": " arddhāṅgulasame vṛtte śrotasī |",
    "T14n1282u_001:50": " tasyā nāsāvaṃso(śo)",
    "T14n1282u_001:51": " nāsāgramavakro vistārārddhāṅgulaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:52": " caturaṅgulaścakṣuḥ koṣaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:53": " tanmadhyamekāṅgulaṃ vistārāt madhye dvyaṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:54": " bhrūvoradhastādārabhyādhaḥ paryantaṃ tryaṅguliḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:55": " cakṣuṣorantare nāsāmūlamekāṅgulaṃ bhrūcaturaṅgulāyatācāpākārā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:56": " arddhāṅgulavistārā madhye vajradharasya |",
    "T14n1282u_001:57": " krodhānāṃ tu kuṭilā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:58": " buddhānāṃ dhyānadṛṣṭīnāṃ dviyavavistārād dvyaṅgulaṣaṭyavādhikāyāmāccāpākāraṃ bodhisattvānāṃ tu caturyavavistārāt viṃśatiyavāyāmādutpalam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:59": " sarvāsāṃ śṛṅgārastrīṇāṃ aṣṭādaśayavāyāmena ṣaṭyavavistārāt matsyodarākāram |",
    "T14n1282u_001:60": " caturyavakaravīraṃ nāsāsamīpaṃ netrāntaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:61": " aparanetrānto'",
    "T14n1282u_001:62": " pāṅgaścaturyavaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:63": " tryaṅgulaścakṣurmaṇiḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:64": " piṭakena dviyavonnataḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:65": " kālikā sātirekapañcayavapramāṇā sṛkkaṇīsūtramādṛṣṭirmadhyeputtalikā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:66": " sārddhaṅgulasyaiva pañcabhāgena vistāreṇaikāṅgulaṃ tārātribhāgikā'",
    "T14n1282u_001:67": " ṅgulasya caturthāṃśaḥ prakāśito akṣiputrakaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:68": " padmapatrākṛti[kāryo]netrakośo'",
    "T14n1282u_001:69": " ṅgulatrayam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:70": " karavīrasamasūtraṃ nāsikāpuṭasya |",
    "T14n1282u_001:71": " tārāsamaṃ cibukaṃ sṛkkaṇī tathā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:72": " bhruvormadhyaṃ sārddhāṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:73": " tatraivorṇṇā ekāṅgulā pūrṇacandranibhā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:74": " nāsā urṇā uṣṇīṣasamaṃ sūtram |",
    "T14n1282u_001:75": " bhruvo rekhāsamau karṇṇau |",
    "T14n1282u_001:76": " āyāmena caturaṅgulau dvyaṅgulavistārau tatpatraṃ ca yavam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:77": " tayorūrdhvapatraṃ caturyavaṃ natamūcemai (muccaire)kāṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:78": " vilaṃ caturyavam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:79": " kapolakarṇacchidrayormadhye karṇṇāvarttaḥ phalikākāro dviyavaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:80": " karṇalatā caturaṅgulī dīrghataḥ sthūlā yathā śobhanā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:81": " pūrvamuṣṇīṣādigrīvāparyantaṃ caturyavādhikaviṃśatyaṅgulamuktvā idānīṃ grīvādigulphādhaḥ paryantasya vibhāgaḥ kriyate |",
    "T14n1282u_001:82": " grīva caturaṅgulā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:83": " grīvāto hṛdayaṃ sārddhadvādaśāṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:84": " hṛdayānnābhiparyantaṃ tathā nābherāguhyaṃ sārddhadvādaśāṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:85": " ūruḥ pañcaviṃśatyaṅgulam,",
    "T14n1282u_001:86": " jaṃghāpi tathā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:87": " jānuḥ ṣaḍaṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:88": " dvyaṅgulo gulphaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:89": " gulphādadhaścaturaṅgulameti samyaksaṃbuddhavajradharabodhisattvādīnāṃ daśatālasya kathito vibhāgaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:90": " anyeṣāṃ tu yathāyogamunneyam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:91": " yathāśobhaṃ śiromaṇirvimalaḥ kāryaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:92": " uṣṇīṣaṃ madhyasthīkṛtya dvādaśāṅgulaṃ jaṭāmakuṭaṃ vajradharasya |",
    "T14n1282u_001:93": " vīrāṇāṃ bodhisattvānāṃ cāṣṭāṅgulaṃ jaṭājūṭaṃ makuṭaṃ ceti viśeṣaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:94": " daśāṅgulamiti kecit |",
    "T14n1282u_001:95": " uṣṇīṣādho veṣṭanena dvādaśāṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:96": " lalāṭoparicchatrākāram |",
    "T14n1282u_001:97": " nīladakṣiṇāvartamūrddhvajam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:98": " unnatamastakāṃ(kaṃ)",
    "T14n1282u_001:99": " karṇasaṃmukhapṛṣṭhaveṣṭanena dvātriṃśadaṅgulamastakam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:100": " grīvā cāṣṭāṅgulavistārā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:101": " tasyā veṣṭanaṃ caturviṃśatyaṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:102": " grīvāyā aṣṭāṅgulaṃ hitvā karṇasamīpe caturaṅgulena saha dvādaśāṅgulaskandhāvṛttaḥ sthāṇukṣoṇānvitaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:103": " kṛśatārahitaskandhāt kaphoṇerurdhvaṃ viṃśatyaṅgulo bāhuḥ kaphoṇirekāṅgulā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:104": " kaphoṇeradhastānmaṇibandhādūrddhvaṃ prabāhuḥ ṣoḍaśāṅgulaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:105": " ekāṅgulo maṇibandhaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:106": " maṇibandhādadho madhyāṅgulyagraparyantaṃ dvādaśāṅgulo hastaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:107": " evaṃ pañcāśadaṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:108": " bāhau madhyeveṣṭanaṃ viṃśatyaṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:109": " upabāhormadhyaveṣṭanaṃ ṣoḍaśāṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:110": " maṇibandhe veṣṭanaṃ dvādaśāṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:111": " maṇibandhāt saptāṅgulaṃ karatalam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:112": " madhyāṅgulī pañcamātrā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:113": " tasyāḥ parvārddhonā pradeśinī |",
    "T14n1282u_001:114": " anāmikā tatsamā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:115": " parvonā kanīyasī |",
    "T14n1282u_001:116": " sarvāṅgulyastriparvāḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:117": " parvārddhena nakhāstāsām |",
    "T14n1282u_001:118": " maṇibandhāccaturaṅgulam tyaktvā nakhāgraṃ yāvaccaturaṅgulo'ṅguṣṭhaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:119": " dviparvaḥ parvārddhena nakhaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:120": " aṅguṣṭho vesṭanena caturaṅgulaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:121": " aṅguṣṭhapradeśinyorantaraṃ tryaṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:122": " maṇibandhāt kanīyasīmūlaparyantaṃ pañcāṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:123": " skandhāt kakṣaparyantaṃ navāṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:124": " kakṣāt stanaṃ yāvat ṣaḍaṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:125": " uraḥpṛṣṭhayorveṣṭanaṃ ṣaṭpañcāśadaṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:126": " stanayormadhyaṃ sārddhadvādaśāṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:127": " stananābhyormadhyaṃ ṣoḍaśāṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:128": " nābhimārabhya vṛṣṭhena (pṛṣṭhena)",
    "T14n1282u_001:129": " sa[ha]nābhiṃ yāvat ṣaṭcatvāriṃśadaṅgulaṃ nābhernimūtayo ekāṅgulaṃ pariṇāhaṃ ca |",
    "T14n1282u_001:130": " tathā vistareṇāṣṭādaśāṅgulā kaṭiḥ sphiccau caturaṅgulau vistārāyāmau |",
    "T14n1282u_001:131": " urumūlayormadhyaṃ dvādaśāṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:132": " veṣṭanena triguṇam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:133": " tayormadhya āyāmena pañcāṅgulau vistāreṇa caturaṅgulau aṇḍakoṣau |",
    "T14n1282u_001:134": " tadupari dvyaṅgulaṃ vistāreṇa guhyaṃ dairghyeṇa dviyavādhika - ṣaḍaṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:135": " urumadhyaṃ veṣṭanena dvātriṃśadaṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:136": " jānuveṣṭanamaṣṭāviṃśatyaṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:137": " jaṃghāmadhyaveṣṭanaṃ caturviṃśatyaṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:138": " jaṃghādho veṣṭanamekaviṃśatyaṅgulam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:139": " pādagrantheradhaḥ pārṣṇī caturaṅgule |",
    "T14n1282u_001:140": " adha ūrdhvataḥ ṣaḍaṅgule |",
    "T14n1282u_001:141": " tiryakvistārācca pariṇāhenāṣṭādaśāṅgule |",
    "T14n1282u_001:142": " gulphātparato'",
    "T14n1282u_001:143": " ṅguṣṭhanakhāgraṃ yā[va]t pādau dvādaśāṅgulau vistāreṇa ṣaḍaṅgulau |",
    "T14n1282u_001:144": " adha ūrdhvena dvyaṅgulavistārau pādayoḥ pārṣṇī |",
    "T14n1282u_001:145": " pādāṅgulyaḥ pañca dvidviparvā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:146": " tāsāṃ madhyaparvārddhena nakhāḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:147": " pādāṅguṣṭhaḥ pañcāṅgulaḥ pariṇāhena dairghyeṇa tryaṅgulaḥ ,",
    "T14n1282u_001:148": " tatsamā pradeśinī |",
    "T14n1282u_001:149": " tasyāḥ sārddhaparvonā madhyamā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:150": " tasyā aṣṭama - bhāgonānāmikā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:151": " tasyā apyaṣṭamabhāgonā kanīyasī |",
    "T14n1282u_001:152": " aṅgulya ekāṅgulonnatāḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:153": " aṅguṣṭhāgrau sārddhāṅgulonnatau |",
    "T14n1282u_001:154": " bahiruparipādau kūrmmapṛṣṭhasamau |",
    "T14n1282u_001:155": " adhastāccakrādi - bhiralaṅkṛtau |",
    "T14n1282u_001:156": " kukkuṭāṇḍatilākāraṃ caturasrañca maṇḍalam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:157": " sarvasāmānyaliṅgānāṃ mukhākṛtiścaturvidhā ||",
    "T14n1282u_001:158": " saṃbuddhānāṃ mahāvajradharāṇāṃ ca mukhaṃ kukkuṭāṇḍākāram |",
    "T14n1282u_001:159": " locanādidevakanyānāṃ tilabimbākāram |",
    "T14n1282u_001:160": " maitreyādimahābodhisattvānāṃ mahāvajradharavanmukham |",
    "T14n1282u_001:161": " kharvalambodarakrodhānāṃ maṇḍalākāraṃ vṛttamukham |",
    "T14n1282u_001:162": " lalitakrodhānāṃ tu bodhisattvavat |",
    "T14n1282u_001:163": " pretādīnāṃ tu caturasraṃ mukham |",
    "T14n1282u_001:164": " lāvaṇyadarśanaṃ mukhadvayam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:165": " caturasramaṇḍalaṃ mukhadvayaṃ vikṛtākāram |",
    "T14n1282u_001:166": " same dṛṣṭi(ṣṭhī)",
    "T14n1282u_001:167": " prasannāsye saumyasnigdhāvalokane |",
    "T14n1282u_001:168": " sārddhena dainyayukte'",
    "T14n1282u_001:169": " dhaḥ kartavye sarvadarśinām ||iti |",
    "T14n1282u_001:170": " locanādi yoginīnāṃ uṣṇīṣaguhyorupṛṣṭhaveṣṭanāt daśāṅgulena saha pīnaghanakucau |",
    "T14n1282u_001:171": " nābhāvaveṣṭanāt daśabhāgaṃ hitvā kaṭisthalaṃ pīnaṃ kartavyam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:172": " bodhisattvamānāduraso daśabhāgena guhyāṃśena ca vīriṇīnā(nāṃ)",
    "T14n1282u_001:173": " kucayugmaṃ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:174": " kaṭisthalaṃ tu pūrvavat |",
    "T14n1282u_001:175": " kākāsyādīnāṃ tattāladvayena stanādau pīnatā |",
    "T14n1282u_001:176": " bhagavataḥ śrīsaṃvarasya pūrvakṛtalakṣaṇe mukhakṣetre caturyavaṃ hitvā dvādaśabhāgikavistāre adhaḥ koṇayorekasārddhadvisārddhadvibhāgaharaṇavarttanāt bhagavato mūlavāmadakṣiṇapaścimavaktrāṇi |",
    "T14n1282u_001:177": " bhagavato dakṣiṇakhagāṇḍamukhavad vajravārāhīkhaṇḍarohārūpiṇīdevakanyānāṃ ca paścimamukhavattilabimbākāraṃ ḍākinyāḥ pūrvamukhavat lāmāyāḥ vāmamukhavat cūtābhaṃ vīravīreśvarīṇāñca |",
    "T14n1282u_001:178": " kākāsyādīnāṃ kākādimukhameva bhagavato vāmadakṣiṇamukhaṃ ca kurvaddhasitatrasitabubhukṣitānāmiveti viśeṣaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:179": " indra - īśānavāyuvaruṇa - upendrapitāmahā navatālāḥ khagāṇḍamukhāḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:180": " vemacitrinairṛtiṣaṭtālāḥ krodhasvabhāvāḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:181": " kuberānalau lalitakharvāvaṣṭatālau khagāṇḍamukhau |",
    "T14n1282u_001:182": " saumyagrahāḥ sūryaśca śakravanmānamānitāḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:183": " krūrāḥ krodhasvabhāvāḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:184": " arddhakāyo rāhuḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:185": " adhaḥkāyanāgākāraḥ ketuḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:186": " sarvanāgā navatālā khagāṇḍamukhāḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:187": " vaṭuvāmanaherambaḥ kartavyaḥ pañcatālikaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:188": " tatra tālaikena mukhaḥ grīvāta āguhyaṃ yāvattāladvayena guhyataḥ pādatalaṃ yāvattāladvayeneti pañcatālam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:189": " tatra saṃbuddhāḥ karuṇābhūtaśāntarasopetāḥ vajradharamukhaṃ sarvaśarīraṃ navarasarasāviṣṭam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:190": " bodhisattvādayastu śṛṅgārarasādhikāḥ iti prastāraḥ kathitaḥ ||",
    "T14n1282u_001:191": " || iti samyaksambuddhabhāṣitaṃ pratimālakṣaṇavivaraṇaṃ samāptam ||",
    "T14n1282u_001:192": " svabhāvāḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:193": " arddhakāyo rāhuḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:194": " adhaḥkāyanāgākāraḥ ketuḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:195": " sarvanāgā navatālā khagāṇḍamukhāḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:196": " vaṭuvāmanaherambaḥ kartavyaḥ pañcatālikaḥ |",
    "T14n1282u_001:197": " tatra tālaikena mukhaḥ grīvāta āguhyaṃ yāvattāladvayena guhyataḥ pādatalaṃ yāvattāladvayeneti pañcatālam |",
    "T14n1282u_001:198": " tatra saṃbuddhāḥ karuṇābhūtaśāntarasopetāḥ vajradharamukhaṃ sarvaśarīraṃ"
}